We loop through each factory in the sorted `factory` array. For each factory, we have a nested loop to repair the robots. We decrement the `limit` of the current factory and increment the `idx` pointer. We add the distance from the current factory to the robot to the result.

Finally, we return the result `res` which represents the minimum total distance traveled by all the robots.
